messages.description: The slow movement of the light in a moderate-sized circle (in either direction) indicates either, 'I am okay, are you okay?' when it is the initial signal, or 'Yes, I am okay, too, thanks for asking' when it's the reply.
The signals for 'Emergency' and 'Attention' are performed by vigorous flashing movements of a diver's light beam in a horizontal or vertical direction.

message_variations: What is the remaining bottom time?

messages.description: A plastic line arrow always points towards an exit with surface with breathable air.
Two plastic line arrows placed back to back mark the spot as the midway distance between two entrances.
